{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01Bs2JBfY2ttQVME3J5r974B","type":"tool_result","content":"31f4eb9 feat(stepml): add shared infrastructure, orchestrator, and updated problem statement\n2671660 docs(stepml): rewrite design doc and macro plan for Round 2\n45f1dab docs(stepml): add E2E latency decomposition to design doc\n2b8e42c docs(stepml): broaden problem scope for Round 2 — all LatencyModel components\n5dac60d refactor(stepml): move Round 1 artifacts into round1/ subdirectory\naeffdd4 docs(stepml): add Round 1 findings summary for future ideation\n64f863e feat(stepml): WP4/5 decision gate — per-experiment XGBoost recommended for integration\n1e9f976 feat(stepml): WP3 experiment code and findings for Ideas 1 & 2\n16e72bc feat(stepml): WP2 hypothesis scaffolding — 3 ideas × 3 sub-hypotheses\nbd3a464 feat(stepml): WP1 research ideation — 3 ideas with 9 reviews + executive summary\n9210b1a feat(stepml): add WP0 baselines and validation — blackbox regression, temporal split, ProgressIndex proxy\nf0839ce feat(stepml): add WP0 shared infrastructure — data loader, splits, evaluation, sampling\nba26f6e fix(roofline): use zero alpha coefficients by default in --roofline mode\n4c82ec0 feat(roofline): integrate roofline v2 with MFU-based step time estimation\n7b59c19 docs: fix governance doc inconsistencies and add missing process guidance (#446)\n20e7af3 docs: add MkDocs Material site for project documentation (#440)\nc1c3271 feat: add --roofline flag for auto-fetch of HuggingFace config.json (#435)\n66a54b7 skill(convergence-review): configurable reviewer model (#439)\n256f322 feat(workload): spec v2 schema + SLO tier expansion (W0-1) (#434)\n80739c0 docs: add public-facing design documentation suite (#429)\n9d33b8b hypothesis: test 3 performance hypotheses -- H27 confirmed, H28 refuted, H29 confirmed (#433)\na95c4bc test(cluster): promote H25/H26 hypothesis findings to Go tests (#427)\n96a0542 docs: fix README documentation drif